value.subject: Microsoft Teams Exploratory trials expire soon

body.content:
Sign in to review expiring trials.
[Microsoft]
Move users to a subscription that includes Microsoft Teams to avoid losing access

There are 0 users that have Microsoft Teams Exploratory trials expiring in the next month. If you want these users to continue using Microsoft Teams after the trial ends, go to the Microsoft 365 admin center and move them to a paid subscription for Microsoft 365.

Move users ><https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Fadmin.microsoft.com%2Fadminportal%2Fhome%3Fsource%3Dtcemail%23%2Fsubscriptions%3FLFT%3Dtrue%26state%3Dactive%26productId%3DCFQ7TTC0J1FV%26skuId%3D0003&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD1ob21l>

Or work with your partner or Microsoft account representative to move them to a paid subscription.

If a user isn’t upgraded to a paid subscription, all services included in their Microsoft Teams Exploratory will end, and your user may lose access to their data stored in Microsoft Teams, OneDrive, and SharePoint. The customer data for all services associated with the Microsoft Teams Exploratory trial will be handled in accordance with the Microsoft Online Subscription Agreement<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Fportal.office.com%2FCommerce%2FMosa.aspx%3Fcc2%3Dus%26cl%3Den%26cc%3Den-us%26gcc%3DFalse&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD1Nb3NhLmFzcHg%3D> and the Product Terms<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Flicensing%2Fterms%2Fwelcome%2Fwelcomepage&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD13ZWxjb21lcGFnZQ%3D%3D>.

You can also choose to let users auto-claim licenses the first time they sign in by creating an Auto-claim policy<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Fadmin.microsoft.com%2FAdminportal%2FHome%3Fsource%3Dtcemail%23%2Flicenses%2Fautoclaimpoliciespage&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD1Ib21l>. This provides users the ability to automatically claim a product license the first time they sign in to an app such as Microsoft Teams.

Additional references

Learn more about managing the Microsoft Teams Exploratory experience<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fmicrosoftteams%2Fteams-exploratory&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD10ZWFtcy1leHBsb3JhdG9yeQ%3D%3D>.

See what’s included in Teams Exploratory trial<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fmicrosoftteams%2Fteams-exploratory&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD10ZWFtcy1leHBsb3JhdG9yeV8y>.

Read information about Microsoft Teams plans and features<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Foffice365%2Fservicedescriptions%2Fteams-service-description&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD10ZWFtcy1zZXJ2aWNlLWRlc2NyaXB0aW9u>.

Learn what happens to your data and access when your subscription ends<https://nam.safelink.emails.azure.net/redirect/?destination=https%3A%2F%2Flearn.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fmicrosoft-365%2Fcommerce%2Fsubscriptions%2Fwhat-if-my-subscription-expires%3Fview%3Do365-worldwide%23what-happens-to-data-when-a-subscription-expires&p=bT1jMTM4ZTBkYi1jODBlLTQ0ZjItYjNhZS1jMTIzNGQ5ZDU4YTEmdT1hZW8mbD13aGF0LWlmLW15LXN1YnNjcmlwdGlvbi1leHBpcmVz>.
